Class AsxOuchFileReferenceDataProvider

  • java.lang.Object

        • com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.ouch.dataproviders.OuchFileReferenceDataProviderBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IReferenceDataProvider, IComponent, IHasAttributes, IConfigurable, IRegisterable, IService

    public class AsxOuchFileReferenceDataProvider
extends OuchFileReferenceDataProviderBase
    ASX Reference Data Provider which retrieves all information from static file provided by ASX.

    Format of the file is constant and similar to the ITCH messages (without timestamp field) The example of static file:

    1,R,13d80001,BHP,BHP BLT FPO [BHP],AU000000BHP4,5,AUD,1,0,0,1,0,0 1,L,BHP,1,1,99 1,L,BHP,5,100,1999 1,L,BHP,10,2000,999999900
